<div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="item active">
            <img src="assets/hero_bg2.gif" alt="Operation Paws for Homes">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
              <%= link_to "Available Dogs", dogs_path, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large", :id => "hero-dog" %>
              <%= link_to "Apply for Adoption", new_adopter_path, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large", :id => "hero-adopt" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
<!--         <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">&lsaquo;</a>
        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="span4 sidekick">
      <h2>Events</h2>
       <p>Looking for the perfect new family member? Want to meet them in person first? Here is your chance!  Join Operation Paws for Homes and meet some wonderful dogs and learn more about how we can find the right dog for you at our next adoption event.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/events">Upcoming Events &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4 sidekick">
      <h2>Adoption Guide</h2>
       <p>Adopting a dog saves lives! You must submit an adoption application, and it will take time to process it. We will interview your references and you. We will support you through the entire process to ensure you find a dog that is right for you. Our adoption fees are explained here. </p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/guide">Adoption Guide &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4 sidekick">
      <h2>Donate</h2>
      <p>Operation Paws for Homes is a 501(c)(3) dog rescue organization that is run entirely by dedicated volunteers who help saves dogs in need. Your generous donations directly help cover the costs of rescuing dogs in need.  We also work hard to support the shelters we work with in the south.  It is only due to the patronage of people like you that we can save dogs and give them a chance to find a forever home.</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&business=donate%40ophrescue%2eorg&lc=US&item_name=Operation%20Paws%20for%20Homes&no_note=0&currency_code=USD&bn=PP%2dDonationsBF%3abtn_donateCC_LG%2egif%3aNonHostedGuest"><img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif"></a></p>
      <div class="fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Operation-Paws-For-Homes/125971917423548" data-send="false" data-width="270" data-show-faces="true" data-font="arial"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>